  ![New Tennis Racquet Series MUSE: Form Follows Fun](https://us.yonex.com/cdn/shop/articles/imagee_f0170f75-66c8-4f4d-b6a9-006633423947.jpg?v=1772412546&width=1100)
  
  Feel inspired with **MUSE**, a new tennis racquet series crafted by Yonex for effortless, stress-free rallying.Designed to enhance comfort and fluidity in every swing, MUSE enables a wide range of players to rediscover the pure enjoyment of every rally.
  
  Cultivated over five years and crafted with Yonex’s renowned materials and craftsmanship, MUSE will launch worldwide in late April 2026, offering smooth handling and efficient power transfer designed to address common sources of mental and physical stress during rallying.
  
  From the very first swing, players will start to build an emotional connection with their MUSE―a racquet that helps them to feel the rally and forget everything else. With Yonex’s most forgiving response to date, MUSE sets a new global standard for comfort, control, and enjoyment on court.
  
  **INNOVATION**
  
  **Synchro Frame―Designed for Effortless Rallying**
  
  At the heart of MUSE is the Synchro Frame, a new structural concept that synchronizes three of Yonex’s core technologies to deliver smooth handling, stable performance, and reduced fatigue.
  
  l  Isometric™
  
  l  Uniform Impact Grommet
  
  l  Energy Flow Shaft
  
  Working together, these technologies improve maneuverability, enhance power transmission, and reduce body stress―allowing players to rally longer with confidence and ease.
  
  **ISOMETRIC™**
  
  A signature Yonex technology that achieves a larger sweet spot. By making the vertical and horizontal strings as close in length as possible, a square-shaped ISOMETRIC™ racquet generates a 7% larger sweet spot compared to a conventional round frame\* and delivers greater control without sacrificing power. This technology has been loved by some of the world’s top players for over 40 years, helping them win numerous titles over the years, and continues to evolve even today.
  
  \*Tested by Yonex
  
  **Uniform Impact Grommet**
  
  The newly developedUniform Impact Grommet features a unique straight-grommet structure at all four corners of the frame. By increasing string movement, it produces a more uniform and forgiving response for both center and off-center hits, enhancing comfort and control during rallies.
  
  **Energy Flow Shaft**
  
  The Energy Flow Shaft is a control-oriented shaft that efficiently transfers power while delivering an easy-to-control feel, despite its slim profile. Featuring a carefully engineered concave shape that balances stiffness and flex, the shaft is further enhanced with Servo Filter—an elastic, highly adhesive material that refines vibration and feel. Together, these elements support smooth power transfer and stable control throughout rallies.
  
  **Designed for Comfort, Flow, and Freedom**
  
  With its refined contours, soft silver tone, and matte finish, MUSE supports a natural playing rhythm while reducing on-court stress. Every design element reflects Yonex’s commitment to performance, comfort, and innovation.
  
  **Product Lineup:**
  
  Find your MUSE in a series that includesfive models.
  
  MUSE 98 / MUSE 100 / MUSE 100L / MUSE 100SL / MUSE 107.
  
  Yonex is also launching theMUSE capsule collection, which matches the design of the racquets and will include bags, shoes, strings and vibration dampeners.
  
  **Launch Details:**
  
  The new tennis racquet series MUSE will be available globally starting in late April 2026.
  
